{"id":399830,"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/42/69/426934.jpg","floor":"#1","group":"靠谱人生茶话会","groupHref":"/group/boring","groupThumb":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/icon/m/000/00/03/364.jpg","message":"<a href=\"https://bgm.tv/group/topic/388010\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener noreferrer\" class=\"l\">上期南极洛徒步记录</a><br>又到了激动的徒步环节！本次楼主利用端午时间来到了四姑娘山进行徒步，主要路线是长坪沟马道（斯古拉寺—木骡子）全程徒步完成<br>山沟徒步是我最喜欢的徒步方式，因为不登山所以这次难度相比上次南极洛简直是幼儿园级别，不过海拔还是维持在大概3300左右，需要一定的体能才能顺利跋涉<br>本次徒步耗时八个半小时（受同行朋友拖累本来还可以再快点），往返路程24km，步数3w8<br>长坪沟还有一种徒步路线是长穿毕（从长坪沟穿越垭口到达毕棚沟，从毕棚沟出景区），这个路线难度较大，需要野营，必须要向导或者跟团才能进行，穿越垭口时会有爬升，海拔在4k以上，以后有机会可以尝试<br>相比之下双桥沟没什么玩的，做大巴到每个景点下车拍照，拍了照去下一个景点，没了（最后两张图在双桥沟拍的）<br><br><img src=\"https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2024/06/09/af947f825b0cc78f.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><img src=\"https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2024/06/09/781b0d29b3506ed6.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><img src=\"https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2024/06/09/af902940e38d1dff.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><img src=\"https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2024/06/09/54351aebea91c865.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><img src=\"https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2024/06/09/ec315780d4ca0396.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><img src=\"https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2024/06/09/efe38ea536543e2f.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt><br><img src=\"https://s3.bmp.ovh/imgs/2024/06/09/2c8e319df3bd3efd.jpg\" class=\"code\" rel=\"noreferrer\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" alt>","time":"2024-6-9 21:23","title":"四姑娘山徒步记录！这次感觉非常爽！","userId":"426934","userName":"火龙果汁","userSign":"(低级趣味无罪)"}